title: How Cord-Cutters Can Choose a Video Streaming Service With Walmart+
summary: As of Sept. 15, Walmart+ members can pick between a subscription to new streaming partner Peacock or longtime partner Paramount+.

title: Business travel and expense startup Navan files for initial public offering in booming deal market
summary: Business travel and expense startup Navan has filed for an initial public offering, reporting an annual revenue rate surpassing $600 million.
